{"tid":1105314,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一開心就領嘢嘞","createTime":"2019-04-13T19:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T18:29:50.000Z","uid":431,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c48705d09a86504e07689464b2891d09d67fdde0","tid":1105314,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好好笑我好好笑 唔知有無笑到出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定嘴角含春<br />\n但係歷久不衰嘅好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇十次都會出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n字字精華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夠我depp往後幾廿年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />至死<br />\n所以我個諗到個原困 應該就係因為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無咁可以忘記但大咗之後就開到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痴撚線啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有貢高就更大個反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以又一個圈咁<br />\n所以都話係避開啲開心就唔會唔開心斬腳趾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吔蕉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咁上下浪費得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！正蠢閪！"},{"pid":"8c09d74df62508f49abdd9f9c1d7089ebc4b2958","tid":1105314,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:08:16.000Z","msg":"有返真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以繼續depp<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aadea8ec8285c2e52232e85736ab50aea33231b","tid":1105314,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:11:00.000Z","msg":"但係我都係認真講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好笑雖則好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑住認真講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda9bdac23a0b041808d8debca64c86538d27387","tid":1105314,"uid":10759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQ22AYm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQ22AYm.png&h=1a6e84dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15bfab78c2e71f9c2d5fef5827f4acb6a73b0a3e","tid":1105314,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T22:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNPP1ak.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNPP1ak.gif&h=f1c8f62a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f4d5f09ee24c8e7d2967822c019b56fc332ee95","tid":1105314,"uid":16118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"h